<th>
<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>Bika 3 <a class="external-link" href="http://www.vanhunks.com/lowveld1/modjadji1.html">Modjadji</a> is Bika's long awaited upgrade to Plone 4 and SQL</p>
<p>The opportunity was used to undertake a massive code restructuring in    the interest of future maintenance and performance, as well as adding    much desired new functionality</p>
</th><th>
<h2 class="Subheading">Feedback</h2>
<p>Don't hesitate to post questions, comments and suggestions to the Bika mailing lists: Bika <a class="external-link" href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?hl=en#%21forum/bika-design">LIMS design</a>, <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-users">Users</a> or <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-developers">Developers</a>. Please log issues in the <a class="external-link" href="http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=browse&amp;group_id=145464&amp;atid=762012">public Bika bug tracker</a> at SourceForge.net</p>
<h3>Code repository</h3>
<p>The freshest code can be find in SVN at <b>https://bika.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/bika/bika3</b></p>
<br /></th><th>
<h3 class="Subheading">Coming soon: Set-up data load scripts</h3>
<p>We are currently working on standardised  spreadsheets that can be used   to populate the LIMS with setup data of  your choice. We hope to have   these pre-populated for each Bika branch,  e.g. Water, Health, etc.</p>
<p>For the purpose of testing, we'll use the scripts to populate this  test   instance with consistent data consisting of the uniform  specifications,   QC, uncertainties, turn-around time, precision, price  etc. for all   Analysis Services</p>
<a class="external-link" href="http://www.bikalabs.com/softwarecenter/bika"></a> </th>
</tr>
