<td scope="col">
<h3 class="Subheading">Known Bugs</h3>
<p>Please treat any part of the system outside of the setup area with caution as none of it has been officially tested</p>
<p>It works everywhere else, but  on Windows Firefox installations,   clicking an Analysis Profile when  creating ARs, does not stick. Please   use the keyboard arrows and  [Enter] key to select a Profile. Dragging   the cursor down onto the  desired Profile without clicking also works</p>
